      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JACOBITE THORN (1) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 19.09 beating Benny Moko. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Can make it back-to-back wins. HEY MARTY (7) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 1.5 lengths second (19.01) behind RUN BINDI RUN at this track. Has won two of five starts from this draw. Expected to be in the finish again. MIDNIGHT HIGHWAY (2) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 1 last run (18.90) at this track. Expected to feature again. WILD ANGELA (5) deserves plenty of thought over this trip.",
